channel.title: People can't connect
channel.description:
Ok first off, I am hosting my server on a VPS. It has been up with no problems since July. This morning I check and I see that nobody is on. I check my forums and everyone says they can't connect anymore. This is weird as nothing has changed. For some reason I CAN connect but no one else can. I have not changed the client.
Why can I connect and not anyone else? [b]Source:[/b] Mezzyscape (Regretting this already) [b]Base:[/b] RS2HD [b]Revision[/b] 562
